Feedback

  When a fatal error occurs within Amplify Texture, an error dump file is generated
  containing critical information to help solve the problem. You may find 
  this file in the root of your assets folder after a critical error:
  
    YourProject\Assets\amperr.dump
   
  Please include this file when reporting fatal errors.

